body: Dear all, I am practicing the honeybee tutorial. I wanna read the radiance file for honeybee_Run Daylight Simulation component, however I couldn't find the connection point. Below is the same honeybee_Run Daylight Simulation component in two different versions. It's easy to find the 'radiance file' connection point in the first one. How about the second one?
